{"tid":1437661,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普:9月與中國貿談或取消","createTime":"2019-08-09T14:57:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T15:28:56.000Z","uid":122604,"like":249,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":74,"replies":[{"pid":"c8e302dea75b8755466a74c1b4f7c19b5111d400","tid":1437661,"uid":122604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:57:35.000Z","msg":"美國總統特朗普表示，美國仍在繼續與中國進行貿易談判，但目前不會達成協議，而9月與中國的談判可能取消。<br />\n<br />\n他續稱，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">美國將不會與華為做生意</span></strong>，美國別無選擇只能採取當前正在採取的行動。<br />\n<br />\n外電引述消息人士指出，因應中方宣布暫停採購美國農產品，華府亦推遲審批美國企業向華為供貨的出口許可。特朗普早前突然宣布，對餘下3000億美元中國進口貨品加徵10%關稅，於9月1日生效。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普又稱，聯儲局應該停止量化緊縮，希望看到減息1厘。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2216777/%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%3A9%E6%9C%88%E8%88%87%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E8%B2%BF%E8%AB%87%E6%88%96%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2216777%2F%25E7%2589%25B9%25E6%259C%2597%25E6%2599%25AE%253A9%25E6%259C%2588%25E8%2588%2587%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E8%25B2%25BF%25E8%25AB%2587%25E6%2588%2596%25E5%258F%2596%25E6%25B6%2588&d=Zo4i0ptUI%2BsV2bg8TrofrLM5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=949c7908\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2216777/%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%3A9%E6%9C%88%E8%88%87%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E8%B2%BF%E8%AB%87%E6%88%96%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88</a>"},{"pid":"2a5abbf91735cede2f29272127b5680a3be3f5e1","tid":1437661,"uid":108337,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:59:59.000Z","msg":"Sir, this way"},{"pid":"8f303c92b4d404e0e02f1092f2580ada17dac13a","tid":1437661,"uid":35580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T15:09:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b450d4263ead5209f3c771927a1f4ba308200b4","tid":1437661,"uid":